---

---

<section class="section privacy" id="privacy">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-header fade-in">
            <h2 class="section-title">Your money, your business</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
                Kakeibo is built with a radical idea: your financial data should
                belong to you and only you. Not to servers, not to advertisers,
                not to anyone.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-grid">
            <div class="privacy-card fade-in">
                <div
                    class="privacy-icon"
                    style="background: rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.1);"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="var(--green)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    >
                        <path d="M2 20h.01"></path><path d="M7 20v-4"
                        ></path><path d="M12 20v-8"></path><path d="M17 20V8"
                        ></path><path d="M22 4v16"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>100% Offline</h3>
                <p>
                    Everything runs on your device. No internet required, no
                    cloud sync, no servers. Your data lives in a local database
                    &mdash; fast, reliable, and completely under your control.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-card fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
                <div
                    class="privacy-icon"
                    style="background: rgba(17, 138, 178, 0.1);"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="var(--blue)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    >
                        <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Privacy first</h3>
                <p>
                    No account creation. No email required. No data collection
                    of any kind. We don't know who you are, what you spend, or
                    how you use the app. And we like it that way.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
                <div
                    class="privacy-icon"
                    style="background: rgba(239, 71, 111, 0.1);"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="var(--red)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    >
                        <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"
                        ></rect><path d="m3 3 18 18"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>No ads, ever</h3>
                <p>
                    You pay once, you get the full app. No banners, no pop-ups,
                    no sponsored content. A clean, distraction-free experience
                    that respects your attention.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-card fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
                <div
                    class="privacy-icon"
                    style="background: rgba(255, 209, 102, 0.1);"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="var(--yellow)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M17.94 17.94A10.07 10.07 0 0 1 12 20c-7 0-11-8-11-8a18.45 18.45 0 0 1 5.06-5.94M9.9 4.24A9.12 9.12 0 0 1 12 4c7 0 11 8 11 8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.16 3.19m-6.72-1.07a3 3 0 1 1-4.24-4.24"
                        ></path>
                        <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Zero tracking</h3>
                <p>
                    No analytics. No telemetry. No usage tracking. We don't have
                    dashboards monitoring your behavior. The app works for you,
                    not the other way around.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .privacy {
        background: var(--bg-elevated);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .privacy-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .privacy-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        padding: var(--space-xl);
        transition: transform var(--transition-normal);
    }

    .privacy-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .privacy-icon {
        width: 52px;
        height: 52px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .privacy-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .privacy-card p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--subtext);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .privacy-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
